  <brief_title>Zimura Compared to Sham in Patients With Autosomal Recessive Stargardt Disease (STGD1)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2b Randomized, Double-masked, Controlled Trial to Establish the Safety and Efficacy of Zimura™ (Complement C5 Inhibitor) Compared to Sham in Subjects With Autosomal Recessive Stargardt Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
