  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and efficacy of Zimura™ (complement factor C5 inhibitor) compared to
      Sham in subjects with autosomal recessive Stargardt disease 1 (STGD1).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
